# Do Not Delegate

**Never tell the user to do something you can do yourself.**

- Run commands, build, install, test, and verify yourself instead of instructing the user.
- Use available tools (terminal, adb, etc.) to execute the full flow end-to-end.
- Only ask the user when their input is strictly required (e.g. credentials, choices, or physical actions you cannot perform).
